{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/8544468-singur-pe-lume", "title": "Singur pe lume", "titleComplete": "Singur pe lume", "description": "Singur pe lume (titlul original Sans famille) este un roman celebru \u00een toat\u0103 lumea, publicat ini\u021bial de Hector Malot \u00een 1880 la editura Hetzel din Paris, patronul ei, Jean-Pierre Hetzel, fiind \u0219i editorul c\u0103r\u021bilor lui Jules Verne. Desenele edi\u021biei princeps erau gravuri executate de E.Bayard. Autorul c\u0103r\u021bii, Hector Malot (1830-1907), a scris peste 70 de volume, dar Singur pe lume este de departe opera lui cea mai cunoscut\u0103, fiind de mai multe ori ecranizat. Actualmente editura Hachette de\u021bine drepturile asupra acestei edi\u021bii.Este istoria unui orfan, micul Remi, care tr\u0103ie\u0219te \u00een casa unei femei, tu\u0219a Barberin, dar so\u021bul acesteia, Jerome, sufer\u0103 un accident grav fiind zidar astfel \u00eenc\u00eet \u00eel \u00eenchiriaz\u0103 pe copil unui proprietar de circ, Vitalis, care d\u0103dea mici reprezenta\u021bii al\u0103turi de un c\u0103\u021bel, Remi, care-i conduce pe Dolce \u0219i Zerbino, al\u021bi c\u0103\u021bei arti\u0219ti \u0219i o maimu\u021b\u0103 dresat\u0103, Sufle\u021bel. Romanul se termin\u0103 \u00een clipa \u00een care Remi reu\u0219e\u0219te s\u0103-\u0219i g\u0103seasc\u0103 cu ajutorul lui Mattia familia \u0219i are o urmare care se nume\u0219te chiar a\u0219a, \u00cen familie.", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1281954850i/8544468.jpg", "genres": ["France", "French Literature", "Novels", "19th Century", "Literature", "Adventure", "Classics", "Childrens", "Young Adult", "Fiction"], "isbn": "6065111066", "isbn13": "9786065111066", "publisher": "Steaua Nordului", "author": ["Hector Malot", "Mirela-Gabriela Papuc"], "publishDate": 1262332800000, "characters": ["Vitalis", "Remi"], "places": ["France"], "ratingHistogram": [155, 426, 2240, 6147, 11503], "r