{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/2429135.The_Girl_with_the_Dragon_Tattoo", "title": "The Girl with the Dragon Tattoo", "titleComplete": "The Girl with the Dragon Tattoo (Millennium, #1)", "description": "Harriet Vanger, a scion of one of Sweden\u2019s wealthiest families disappeared over forty years ago. All these years later, her aged uncle continues to seek the truth. He hires Mikael Blomkvist, a crusading journalist recently trapped by a libel conviction, to investigate. He is aided by the pierced and tattooed punk prodigy Lisbeth Salander. Together they tap into a vein of unfathomable iniquity and astonishing corruption.An international publishing sensation, Stieg Larsson\u2019s The Girl with the Dragon Tattoo combines murder mystery, family saga, love story, and financial intrigue into one satisfyingly complex and entertainingly atmospheric novel.", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1684638853i/2429135.jpg", "genres": ["Crime", "Fiction", "Adult", "Sweden", "Novels", "Thriller", "Mystery Thriller", "Mystery", "Suspense", "Contemporary"], "isbn": "0670069019", "isbn13": "9780670069019", "publisher": "Viking Canada", "series": ["Millennium"], "author": ["Stieg Larsson", "Reg Keeland"], "publishDate": 1222153200000, "characters": ["Christer Malm", "Gustaf Morell", "Mikael Blomkvist", "Anita Vanger", "Jan K\u00f6bin", "Gottfried Vanger", "Harriet Vanger", "Erika Berger", "Cecilia Vanger", "Isabella Vanger", "Hans-Erik Wennerstr\u00f6m", "Henrik Vanger", "Lisbeth Salander", "Dragan Armansky", "Holger Palmgren", "Birger Vanger", "Dirch Frode", "Nils Bjurman", "Martin Vanger"], "places": ["Sweden", "Stockholm", "Hedestad, Stockholm", "Hedeby Island"], "ratingHistogram": [88072, 125810, 431068, 1048675, 1476195], "ratingsCount": 3169820, "reviewsCount": 77378, "numPages": 480, "language": "English", "awards": [{"name": "Barry Award", "awardedAt": 1262332800000, "category": "Mystery/Crime Novel