{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/6895169-roman-e-pentru-mai-t-rziu", "title": "Roman\u021be pentru mai t\u00e2rziu", "titleComplete": "Roman\u021be pentru mai t\u00e2rziu", "description": "Ion Minulescu a fost cel care a \u00eemp\u0103m\u00e2ntenit la noi un mod de via\u0163\u0103 simbolist \u2014 sintez\u0103 \u00eentre boem\u0103 \u015fi dandism. Adic\u0103 acea voit\u0103 diferen\u0163iere de lumea comun\u0103, prin ceea ce s-a numit atunci \u201espiritul decadent\u00a8. [...] Ce aducea nou Ion Minulescu \u00een poezie? \u00cen primul r\u00e2nd, o alt\u0103 lume, o alt\u0103 surs\u0103 de inspira\u0163ie; nu satul, ci ora\u015ful, nu un univers cantonat \u00een vechime, ci unul modern. Frumuse\u0163ea liricii lui Ion Minulescu a constat \u00een faptul c\u0103 poetul a \u0163intit \u015fi a izbutit s\u0103 r\u0103m\u00e2n\u0103 el \u00eensu\u015fi, cu tot ce a adus nou \u015fi personal \u00een literatura rom\u00e2n\u0103. Iar atunci c\u00e2nd \u015fi-a extins aria inspira\u0163iei, s-a p\u0103strat \u00een matca proprie. A c\u0103utat s-o l\u0103rgeasc\u0103, iar apele s-au dus la vale \u015fi mai zglobii, \u015fi mai nep\u0103s\u0103toare. Chiar dac\u0103 unii cu care a pornit la drum l-au \u00eentrecut, chiar dac\u0103 dintre cei care-au venit dup\u0103 el c\u00e2\u0163iva au aflat c\u0103i mai ad\u00e2nci de expresie. Ion Minulescu nu \u015fi-a pierdut identitatea.- Valeriu R\u00e2peanu", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1355743169i/6895169.jpg", "genres": ["Romanian Literature", "Romania", "20th Century", "Poetry"], "asin": "9736756688", "isbn": "9736756688", "isbn13": "9789736756689", "publisher": "Litera ", "author": ["Ion Minulescu"], "publishDate": 1230796800000, "ratingHistogram": [1, 16, 47, 110, 186], "ratingsCount": 360, "reviewsCount": 9, "numPages": 400, "language": "Romanian"}
