{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/13106932-c-nt-rea-a-cheal-lec-ia-scaunele-regele-moare", "title": "C\u00e2nt\u0103rea\u021ba cheal\u0103. Lec\u021bia. Scaunele. Regele moare", "titleComplete": "C\u00e2nt\u0103rea\u021ba cheal\u0103. Lec\u021bia. Scaunele. Regele moare", "description": "\u201eS-a spus c\u0103 sunt un scriitor al absurdului; exist\u0103 pe lume cuvinte care trec din gur\u0103 \u00een gur\u0103, e \u015fi \u0103sta un cuv\u00e2nt la mod\u0103, care se va demoda. Oricum, el e de pe-acum suficient de vag pentru a nu mai \u00eensemna nimic \u015fi pentru a defini totul. Dac\u0103 nu voi fi uitat, peste c\u00e2tva timp, va exista un alt cuv\u00e2nt care va trece din gur\u0103 \u00een gur\u0103, un alt cuv\u00e2nt primit de-a gata, care ne va defini pe mine \u015fi pe al\u0163ii, f\u0103r\u0103 s\u0103 ne defineasc\u0103. De fapt, existen\u0163a lumii mi se pare nu absurd\u0103, ci de necrezut, \u00eens\u0103 \u00eenl\u0103untrul existen\u0163ei \u015fi al lumii se poate vedea limpede, pot fi descoperite legi \u015fi stabilite reguli \u00abrezonabile\u00bb. Ne\u00een\u0163elesul nu apare dec\u00e2t atunci c\u00e2nd te \u00eentorci la izvoarele existen\u0163ei, c\u00e2nd te a\u015fezi pe margine \u015fi o prive\u015fti \u00een \u00eentregul ei.\u201c (Eug\u00e8ne IONESCO)", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1322217945i/13106932.jpg", "genres": ["Plays", "Romanian Literature", "Classics", "Theatre"], "asin": "9735026937", "isbn": "9735026937", "isbn13": "9789735026936", "publisher": "Humanitas", "author": ["Eug\u00e8ne Ionesco", "Vlad Zografi", "Vlad Russo"], "publishDate": 1262332800000, "ratingHistogram": [7, 10, 36, 88, 127], "ratingsCount": 268, "reviewsCount": 10, "numPages": 240, "language": "Romanian"}
