{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/88514.Platform", "title": "Platform", "titleComplete": "Platform", "description": "In his new work, Michel Houellebecq combines erotic provocation with a terrifying vision of a world teetering between satiety and fanaticism, to create one of the most shocking, hypnotic, and intelligent novels in years.In his early forties, Michel Renault skims through his days with as little human contact as possible. But following his father\u2019s death he takes a group holiday to Thailand where he meets a travel agent\u2014the shyly compelling Val\u00e9rie\u2014who begins to bring this half-dead man to life with sex of escalating intensity and audacity. Arcing with dreamlike swiftness from Paris to Pattaya Beach and from sex clubs to a terrorist massacre, Platform is a brilliant, apocalyptic masterpiece by a man who is widely regarded as one of the world\u2019s most original and daring writers.", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1328330240i/88514.jpg", "genres": ["Sexuality", "21st Century", "France", "French Literature", "Novels", "Roman", "Literature", "Travel", "Fiction", "Contemporary"], "asin": "1400030269", "isbn": "1400030269", "isbn13": "9781400030262", "publisher": "Vintage", "author": ["Michel Houellebecq", "Frank Wynne"], "publishDate": 1089702000000, "characters": ["Val\u00e9rie", "Jean-Yves", "Michel Renault"], "places": ["Paris", "Thailand"], "ratingHistogram": [529, 1553, 5440, 9263, 5798], "ratingsCount": 22583, "reviewsCount": 1426, "numPages": 259, "language": "English"}
